.purchase
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-6.col-xs-offset-3.animated.fadeInLeft
        .row
          %h1 BOOK WITH US IN 60 SECONDS!
          %form{:action => '../postcodes.php', :method => 'post'}
            .col-xs-7.col-xs-offset-1
              %input{:type => 'text', :name => 'postcode', :placeholder => 'Post Code'}
            .col-xs-4= link_to('Book Now!', price_grid_path, :type => 'button', :class => 'btn btn-success')

.container.content
  .row.margin-bottom-30
    .col-md-4
      %h4 Elite service
      %ul.list-unstyled.margin-bottom-20
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          Professional, background checked teams
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          Quick and easy online booking
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          No minimum recurring contracts
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          Satisfaction guaranteed

    .col-md-4
      %h4 Clean & Green
      %ul.list-unstyled.margin-bottom-20
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          Green and eco friendly cleaning products
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          The safest clean possible to protect your family and pets
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          Special requests? We'll make it happen!
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          Fully insured to protect your home

    .col-md-4
      %h4 Easily Available
      %ul.list-unstyled.margin-bottom-20
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          Book online in 60 seconds
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          Flat rate pricing; no need to describe your house to us.
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          No need for a quote, just pick your slot and we'll turn up, rain or shine!
        %li
          %i.fa.fa-check.color-green
          Simple, easy to understand packages

    .row.margin-bottom-30
      .col-md-12.md-margin-bottom-40
        .headline
          %h2 Why Use Maid In Sheffield?
        .row
          .col-sm-4
            = image_tag('mis-transparent-medium.png', class: 'img-responsive margin-bottom-20')
          .col-sm-8
            %p Our mission is to simplify your life by offering convenient and an exceptional quality domestic house cleaning and maid service in Sheffield and the surrounding area. We offer a variety of services and guarantee all work or your money back
            %ul.list-unstyled.margin-bottom-20
              %li
                %i.fa.fa-thumbs-up.color-green
                We don't require a minimum contract; we can do one off emergency cleans or routine cleans, its completely up to you.
              %li
                %i.fa.fa-thumbs-up.color-green
                We're competitive on price because we don't work slowly to make up the hours. Your clean will take approximately 2-3 hours and we send a team of two maids to make sure you get the best clean possible.
              %li
                %i.fa.fa-thumbs-up.color-green
                We only use green and Eco-friendly cleaning products to make sure that our cleans are safe for your family and your pets. We specialise in hypo-allergenic cleaning and we can ensure any special requests are carried out.
              %li
                %i.fa.fa-thumbs-up.color-green
                If you're not happy with your service, we send a team out to make it right. If you're still not happy enough to recommend us to a friend, we offer a full refund.
              %li
                %i.fa.fa-thumbs-up.color-green
                Our uniformed staff are fully insured and background checked to make you feel safe about using our service.

      .col-sm-12
        .headline
          %h2 How It Works
        .col-xs-12{:style => 'text-align: center'}= image_tag('simple_service.png')
        .col-md-4.col-xs-12= link_to(image_tag('pick_service.png'), price_grid_path)
        .col-md-4.col-xs-12= link_to(image_tag('book_service.png'), booking_form_path)
        .col-md-4.col-xs-12= link_to(image_tag('enjoy_service.png'), testimonials_path)

      .col-xs-12.thumbnail-style
        #lieslider.owl-carousel.owl-theme
          .item
            %h3 <br>"Thank you for organising a brilliant clean this morning for my son's flat in Bents Green. <br> A wonderful service and we will use you again soon." <br> - Judi J
          .item
            %h3 <br>"A perfect clean and all the windows look lovely!<br>So impressed with what you were able to do in a short time frame." <br> - Helen E, Hillsborough
          .item
            %h3 <br>"I was a bit hesitant at first to go with a website I'd not used before, <br>but the checklist made it clear what I was getting, and it all worked out great!" <br> - James P, Totley

